=======================================================

AURA SENTINEL MONOREPO(for collaborators).gitignore

Unified file to ignore dependencies for Java,

Python, and Node (Angular) across Windows/Linux/macOS environments.

=======================================================

1. SECURITY: Keys and Credentials (CRITICAL)

The .env file contains the Gemini API key and internal credentials.

/aura-sentinel-intelligence/.env
/aura-sentinel-frontend/.env

2. JAVA / MAVEN (Gateway and Agent Modules)

Ignore all Maven build directories

target/

Logs generated by Spring Boot or Java

*.log
.log.
*.war
*.ear
*.zip
*.rar

IDE Files (IntelliJ, Eclipse, VS Code, etc.)

.idea/
.vscode/
*.iml
.DS_Store

3. NODE / ANGULAR (Frontend Module)

Dependency and local cache directory

/aura-sentinel-frontend/node_modules
/aura-sentinel-frontend/npm-debug.log
/aura-sentinel-frontend/dist/
/aura-sentinel-frontend/tmp/
/aura-sentinel-frontend/coverage/

Angular cache files

/aura-sentinel-frontend/.angular/
/aura-sentinel-frontend/*.tsbuildinfo

4. PYTHON (Intelligence Module)

Virtual environment directories and files

/aura-sentinel-intelligence/venv
/aura-sentinel-intelligence/pycache/
/aura-sentinel-intelligence/.pytest_cache/
/aura-sentinel-intelligence/pip-log.log
*.pyc

5. VS CODE (General)

.history/